The paper deals with the problem of detecting and recognizing Chinese text in natural images, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The authors also mention the use of deep learning methods, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the creation of a large dataset, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR).
